## Migrate legacy subscriptions

For sites that used Voxel Membership plans before 1.7 update, and have active subscribers, there’s an easy way to convert those subscriptions to the new system. You can convert legacy membership plans to either the [new version of membership plans](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_membership-plans_.md), or convert them to [paid listing plans](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_paid-listings-addon_.md), depending which feature you are using from 1.7.

### Instructions

1\. Go to **WP-admin > Paid Members > Members**. If a member has an active Legacy plan, click “Migrate now” link

![](data:image/png;base64,)

2\. Under Migration strategy, choose if you want to convert to paid membership plan, or a paid listing plan.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

3\. If you choose to convert to a paid listing plan, you then select a listing plan you have made available on that site, and press Migrate.
